data.title: Children’s Ministry
data.meta_description: Rock Kids Ministry offers hope to all volunteers, children, and parents by presenting the truths of God's Word through age appropriate resources.
data.text:
Hello, families!

Our Rock Kids mission is to help kids:

KNOW GOD, GROW IN GOD, AND SHOW GOD TO OTHERS!

In an effort to be the best stewards of the ministry God has entrusted to us, we are re–evaluating our summer programs to best support our mission. As such, we will not be holding Camp Rock for the summer of 2016.
